(ii) The voltage induced in secondary side is determined by turns ratio and primary voltage.

We have the relationship,



Now, Voltage on secondary side = (N2/N1) * Primary voltage

Therefore, the voltage induced in the secondary side of the transformer is 1250 volts.

i1 + i2 â i3 â i4 â i5 + i6 = 0 â¦â¦â¦ (1)

The direction of incoming currents to a node is taken as positive while the outgoing currents are taken as negative.
 The reverse of this can also be taken, i.e. incoming current as negative or outgoing as positive.

The equation (1) can also be written as:

i1 + i2 + i6 = i3 + i4 + i5

Sum of incoming currents = Sum of outgoing currents

According to the Kirchhoffâs Current Law, the algebraic sum of the currents entering a node must be

Subject: Prayer For Reconsidering Tuition Fees and Online Activities of Private Universities of Bangladesh During Corona Pandemic.

Body:
Sir, 
Take our greetings. We hope you are well by the grace of Almighty. We would like to draw your kind attention to an important fact. 
We, the students of â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦, are astonished after getting the news about the declaration of online classes, examinations and also starting the new semester. It is really miserable for us. Most of our students can not attend the classes because of some difficulties. In this situation, we are not prepared enough for online classes. Everyday the number of Corona affected people is rising. People are getting scared. 
This online class system is new to most of us as well as our faculty members. We do not feel so comfortable with this as we are not trained enough. We face problems due to electricity issues, wifi issues from both the faculty sides and the student side. In this current situation, we do not even think about our final examinations. 
Now, many of our students are in rural areas. In rural areas, they do not have much internet facilities. They have to buy extra internet packages. For each class, almost 1 GB package is needed to attend the class. It is really tough for us as most of us belong to middle class family. We are not able to afford this anymore. Besides, to recharge, we have to go outside in this lockdown. Unexpectedly, we are bound to contribute spreading the fear of Covid-19. We really feel so disappointed.
We were promising that, UGC may solve the problem. But we think this is not the way to solve the problem. We need your intervention to solve the problem. It will be much beneficial for us. Please, take a good look in these issues. Consider these issues again and again.
Please, do not let us suffer.
